name: Large Sunny room w/ King bed (Boston Harbor Room)
description:
Large Sunny room with king size bed. Tv with access to Netflix.
Located just 10 minutes walk from South Bay shopping center (groceries, AMC movie theater, Starbucks, Loft, Nike, Target, Best Buy and restaurants)
Walking distance to 2 subway lines (the Red Line, 20 minutes )
Walking distance to the Fairmount commuter rail line (5 minutes)
10 minute Uber ride to Downtown and 5 minutes to the seaport depending on traffic.

Guest access
Shared bathroom
Fully equipt kitchen with complementary coffee and tea
